{"tid":2509227,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九巴6死慘劇｜死者母親永不原諒肇事司機：攞去槍斃呀？香港冇得槍斃㗎！","createTime":"2021-04-29T09:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:42:53.000Z","uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f85603f75821561f2dc8a690a1537e652a545907","tid":2509227,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"九巴6死慘劇｜死者母親永不原諒肇事司機：攞去槍斃呀？香港冇得槍斃㗎！<br />\n<br />\n前年粉嶺公路六死38傷九巴車禍，肇事車長文志光早前承認危駕導致他人死亡及身體嚴重受傷兩罪，今被判囚4年及停牌5年。慘劇未隨判刑落幕，生者仍時刻哀傷度日。其中最年輕死者陳嘉龍的母親，最近因台灣太魯閣號車禍而失眠，聽到別人討論仍心有餘悸，「一講就會諗返起個仔」。她認為任何刑責皆不能彌補喪子之痛，「永遠原諒唔到個司機，亦原諒唔到九巴呢間公司，佢（車長）孭咗咁多條命，係咪，唉，攞去槍斃呀？香港冇得槍斃㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210428/QBDQ7CDYFFDZJORNRXPCXIOLGY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210428%2FQBDQ7CDYFFDZJORNRXPCXIOLGY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHweyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=92fcf20f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210428%2FQBDQ7CDYFFDZJORNRXPCXIOLGY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=eab4a397\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210428/QBDQ7CDYFFDZJORNRXPCXIOLGY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">阿龍生前心願，是帶內地未婚妻阿青到國外旅行見識，其年長3歲的姊姊，亦替弟弟圓夢，去年初與龍媽一行三人到韓國旅遊散心，阿青現仍經常與她透過微信聯絡，「佢話要做我個女，我話我有女，佢話做我細女」，算是哀痛中的一點樂。</span>"},{"pid":"eb4501d752ea7ee8f2889b7c9242696f160316f9","tid":2509227,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"阿龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\